 DemoNuGridStyles connected;values;F;colTitles;rowTitles;cellWidths;cellTypes
 EWC.CONNECTED‚Üêconnected
 ‚éïPW‚Üê1000

‚çù NuGrid Styles Demo - Tests: ColTitleBCol/FCol, RowTitleBCol/FCol,
‚çù BCol, FCol, CellFonts, ShowInput (scalar + vector)

 F‚Üê'F1'
 F eWC'Form' 'NuGrid Styles Demo'(50 50)(550 700)('Coord' 'Pixel')

‚çù Create sample data: 4 rows x 4 columns
‚çù Columns: Name (Edit), Score (Numeric Edit), Active (Checkbox), Grade (Label)
 values‚Üê4 4‚ç¥‚ç¨
 values[1;]‚Üê'Alice' 95 1 'A'
 values[2;]‚Üê'Bob' 82 0 'B'
 values[3;]‚Üê'Carol' 71 1 'C'
 values[4;]‚Üê'Dave' 88 1 'B'

 colTitles‚Üê'Name' 'Score' 'Active' 'Grade'
 rowTitles‚Üê‚ç≥4
 cellWidths‚Üê100 80 70 70

‚çù Create Font objects for CellFonts
 (F,'.FontA')eWC'Font'('PName' 'Courier New')('Size' 14)('Weight' 700)
 (F,'.FontB')eWC'Font'('PName' 'Arial')('Size' 12)('Italic' 1)
 (F,'.FontC')eWC'Font'('PName' 'Arial')('Size' 11)
 (F,'.FontD')eWC'Font'('PName' 'Arial')('Size' 13)('Underline' 1)

‚çù Create the NuGrid with styling properties
 (F,'.G')eWC'NuGrid'('Posn'(80 20))('Size'(180 360))('Values' values)('ColTitles' colTitles)('RowTitles' rowTitles)('CellWidths' cellWidths)('TitleWidth' 40)('CurCell'(1 1))('VScroll' ¬Ø1)
‚çù Header colours: dark blue column headers with white text
 (F,'.G')eWS'ColTitleBCol'(0 51 102)
 (F,'.G')eWS'ColTitleFCol'(255 255 255)
‚çù Row headers: dark green with white text
 (F,'.G')eWS'RowTitleBCol'(0 102 51)
 (F,'.G')eWS'RowTitleFCol'(255 255 255)
‚çù Grid-wide foreground colour (dark blue text on data cells)
 (F,'.G')eWS'FCol'(0 0 128)

‚çù Create Input components
 (F,'.G.E1')eWC'Edit'
 (F,'.G.E2')eWC'Edit'('FieldType' 'Numeric')
 (F,'.G.B1')eWC'Button'('Style' 'Check')('Caption' '')
 (F,'.G.L1')eWC'Label'

‚çù Set up Input and CellTypes
 (F,'.G')eWS'Input'((F,'.G.E1')(F,'.G.E2')(F,'.G.B1')(F,'.G.L1'))
 cellTypes‚Üê4 4‚ç¥1 2 3 4
 (F,'.G')eWS'CellTypes' cellTypes

‚çù BCol: per-cellType background colours (indexed by cellType-1)
‚çù Type1=light yellow, Type2=light blue, Type3=light green, Type4=light grey
 (F,'.G')eWS'BCol'((255 255 220)(220 235 255)(220 255 220)(240 240 240))

‚çù CellFonts: per-cellType font objects (indexed by cellType-1)
 (F,'.G')eWS'CellFonts'((F,'.FontA')(F,'.FontB')(F,'.FontC')(F,'.FontD'))

‚çù ShowInput: vector - show Edit and Checkbox always, Numeric and Label only on select
‚çù Type1=Edit(show), Type2=Numeric(hide), Type3=Checkbox(show), Type4=Label(hide)
 (F,'.G')eWS'ShowInput'(1 0 1 0)

‚çù Add event handlers (reuse CBNuGrid)
 (F,'.G')eWS'Event'(‚äÇ'CellMove' 'CBNuGrid')
 (F,'.G')eWS'Event'(‚äÇ'CellChanged' 'CBNuGrid')

‚çù Info labels
 (F,'.Info1')eWC'Label' 'NuGrid Styles: ColTitleBCol/FCol, RowTitleBCol/FCol, BCol, FCol, CellFonts, ShowInput'(20 20)(20 660)
 (F,'.Info2')eWC'Label' 'ShowInput=(1 0 1 0): Edit+Checkbox always visible, Numeric+Label only on select'(45 20)(20 660)

‚çù Event log
 (F,'.LogTitle')eWC'Label' 'Event Log:'(280 20)(20 100)
 (F,'.Log')eWC'Label' '(Events will appear here)'(300 20)(220 660)
